com.pstmetro.dijkstra

Interface DijkstraConnection<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - The type of the Nodes, in this case a DijkstraConnection<MetroNode> would be created.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MetroConnection

    public interface DijkstraConnection<V>
    This interface details a 1 way connection from the source to the destination on a DijkstraMap. Implementing Generics allows us to specify any type of node. Making this class an interface allows us to perhaps add visual artifacts to the connections if they are necessary.
